{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Stop inheritance tax on Life insurance",
        "additional_details": "Especially if the tragedy were to happen early in life, the young families could have limited options to survive. \r\nMaking a plan to mitigate such risk, the individual is showing responsible behaviour not only towards their family but also the society by avoiding them becoming a burden.\r\n\r\nAnd this policy to include Life Insurance in Inheritance tax penalizes the responsible behaviour.",
        "background": "Life insurance is part of inheritance tax calculations.\r\nThe purpose of Insurance is to provide for the dependents of a bread earner of a family when worst happens. The young families could have limited options and end up being dependent on System.\r\nThis policy penalizes the responsible behavior.",
